rating_comment: Wasn't able to go to his place as my stay in Gangtok got delayed due to roadblocks and had texted the same to him 4 days beforehand but he refused to give any refund at all. Though I understand there was no refund policy while booking but atleast 30-50% of refund was mandated as I have had similar experience in otherstays and they have provided complete refunds. No offense to the host, but my experience was bad

A nice little room which is clean & hygienic.
Hosts are extremely sweet & highly cooperative.
Some improvements can be made (wash basin, geyser) but not a big deal for a short stay.
Great quick stop if you are planning to catch a flight at Bagdogra airport. Abhishek and his family were very accommodating and proactive in their communication.
Wonderful family Abhishek, didi and aunty. Almost like a home would definitely visit next time I'm there. Stay safe mate.
